.TH LOA-INTERESTS-SET 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
interests set \- Configure smart reading interests
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> interests set
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Starts an interactive prompt to configure recommendation interests.
.TP
Supports genres, tags, authors, minimum rating, preferred location, and unread preference.
.TP
Blank input keeps current value. Type \fBnone\fR to clear a field. Type \fBcancel\fR to abort.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> interests set
.SH SEE ALSO
loa(1), loa-interests-show(1), loa-reading-smart-preview(1), loa-reading-smart-generate(1)
